{"tid":2448806,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周竪峰李志宏等灣仔扒房參與結婚派對　警凌晨票控28人違限聚令","createTime":"2021-03-16T07:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T08:07:06.000Z","uid":173921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc7aff7c71a54039d09702483592d477906e996","tid":2448806,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXEYugv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXEYugv.jpg&h=cdd2394a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚（15日）8時許，有近30人疑於灣仔交加里一間「黃店」扒房內聚集參與結婚派對，沙田區議員李志宏及中大學生會前會長周竪峰等有份出席，至晚上10時許仍未散場，有人向警方報案。大批警員到場時，該扒房拉上捲閘，警員未有破門或拍門，一直在店外等候。<br />\n<br />\n至今（16日）凌晨2時45分，警員拍門要求店內的人開門，有人應門稱前門無法開啟，着警員到後門。警員及後經後門進入店內，向場內14男14女（23至63歲）發限聚令告票，至凌晨4時許帶走涉違反營業令的41歲姓馬店主。<br />\n<br />\n周竪峰離開現場時稱「冇嘢回應」，李志宏則稱自己沒有違法下被票控，向警員解釋時對方僅稱「有咩同法官講」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210316/s00001/1615858149029/%E5%91%A8%E7%AB%AA%E5%B3%B0%E6%9D%8E%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%8F%E7%AD%89%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%89%92%E6%88%BF%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A728%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%95%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210316%2Fs00001%2F1615858149029%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E7%25AB%25AA%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25AE%258F%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%2589%2592%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A728%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2595%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=dde52bfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210316%2Fs00001%2F16158581